-- 2010-11-10T17:35:10Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-10/cardiac-science-sued-by-investor-over-opto-circuits-2-30-a-share-buyout.html
Cardiac Science Corp., a maker of
heart-treatment devices, was sued in Delaware Chancery Court by
an investor contending stockholders are being shortchanged in a
planned $2.30 per share buyout by Opto Circuits India Ltd.  To contact the reporter on this story:
